text: The Batth people are mainly found in Haryana, Punjab and Pakistan Punjab, Gujranwala. They are not related to the “Butt” community found in Pakistan, who are of Kashmiri descent. ==References== Category:Jat clans of Pakistan Category:Jat clans of Punjab Category:Jat clans of Rajasthan Category:Jat clans of Haryana
